iki/Special:EntityPage/Q92760#sitelinks-wikipedia \"Edit interlanguage links\")\n  * [Article](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claude_Shannon \"View the content page \\[alt-c\\]\")\n  * [Talk](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:Claude_Shannon \"Discuss improvements to the content page \\[alt-t\\]\")\n\n\nEnglish\n  * [Read](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claude_Shannon)\n  * [Edit](https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Claude_Shannon&action=edit \"Edit this page \\[alt-e\\]\")\n  * [View history](https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Claude_Shannon&action=history \"Past revisions of this page \\[alt-h\\]\")\n\n\nTools\nTools\nmove to sidebar hide\nActions \n  * [Read](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claude_Shannon)\n  * [Edit](https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Claude_Shannon&action=edit \"Edit this page \\[alt-e\\]\")\n  * [View history](https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Claude_Shannon&action=history)\n\n\nGeneral \n  * [What links here](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:WhatLinksHere/Claude_Shannon \"List of all English Wikipedia pages containing links to this page \\[alt-j\\]\")\n  * [Related changes](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:RecentChangesLinked/Claude_Shannon \"Recent changes in pages linked from this page \\[alt-k\\]\")\n  * [Upload file](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:File_Upload_Wizard \"Upload files \\[alt-u\\]\")\n  * [Permanent link](https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Claude_Shannon&oldid=1355187103 \"Permanent link to this revision of this page\")\n  * [Page information](https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Claude_Shannon&action=info \"More information about this page\")\n  * [Cite this page](https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:CiteThisPage&page=Claude_Shannon&id=1355187103&wpFormIdentifier=titleform \"Information on how to cite this page\")\n  * [Get shortened URL](https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:UrlShortener&url=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FClaude_